reviewText: The rabbi is very intelligent. I enjoyed the DVD.

Rabbi Funnye is answering some very good and very "uncomfortable" questions with so much grace and dignity. This interview captures, in my mind, some beautiful things about the Jewish Soul.  Please watch and enjoy. Above all, learn.  Blessings and Shalom.

I'm not sure what to say about this. I guess it was a good interview since it kept my attention. Yet I couldn't help feel it was an interrogation. On the hand, the questions were what people wanted to know. The Rabbi answered candidly which I appreciated. So I gave it 3 stars.
